{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"bind-slice-mire","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n\n1. A rebar store previously synced/bound to the **DIG** Jira project (bindings +\n   `dig-####` rebar-id labels baked into event history).\n2. Re-point sync at a different project: `rebar.toml [jira] project = \"REB\"`.\n3. `rebar reconcile --mode dry-run`.\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n\n- **Expected:** with `jira.project = REB`, the reconciler syncs against REB only\n  (or refuses, surfacing the project mismatch).\n- **Actual:** the plan targets **DIG**: 1,018 / 1,415 planned mutations point at\n  `DIG-####` keys (977 outbound UPDATEs + DIG-keyed creates); `reconcile-check`\n  reports 978 unbound **DIG** issues on the inbound side even though REB is empty.\n  Verified on navasage: DIG is the live DSO project (e.g. DIG-5805 is DSO's own\n  canary bug) — a live pass would mutate real DSO issues.\n\n## Root cause\n\n`jira.project` only governs the CREATE project for *unbound* tickets. Tickets\nalready bound (binding store `.tickets-tracker/.bridge_state/bindings.json`:\n62 confirmed DIG bindings) or carrying `dig-####` labels keep targeting DIG. There\nis no cross-project guard and no supported \"re-target to a new project\" migration.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] The reconciler refuses (or loudly warns + skips) when a planned outbound\n      mutation targets a Jira key whose project ≠ configured `jira.project`\n      (cross-project safety guard, fail-closed).\n- [ ] The inbound fetch is scoped to `jira.project` (REB), not the whole instance / DIG.\n- [ ] A documented path to re-target an existing store to a new project (clear/rebind\n      bind-state + strip stale rebar-id labels), so a clean REB mirror can be built.\n- [ ] Re-running the dry-run after migration shows 0 mutations targeting DIG.","id":"626d-0c60-0b4f-49ed","parent_id":"","priority":0,"tags":["jira-sync","reconciler","safety"],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"Reconciler targets DIG despite jira.project=REB — stale DIG bindings/labels + no cross-project guard"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782414631737351001,"uuid":"aa895707-9511-49f8-9464-fdbbdfec70f4"}